  <!-- INTENSITY TOOLS -->
  <div class="pfg-sec-break"><span>MEASURING</span> Intensity — RPE Scale</div>

  <div class="pfg-card pfg-strip-blue">
    <div class="pfg-card-head"><div class="pfg-card-icon" style="background:rgba(42,95,158,0.1);">📊</div><h3>Rate of Perceived Exertion (RPE) — Modified Borg 1-10</h3></div>
    <p style="font-size:13px;margin-bottom:12px;">Use RPE when you don't have a client's 1-RM yet, or to autoregulate intensity. More practical than % 1-RM for daily use.</p>
    <div class="pfg-rpe-row">
